title: Episode 10 w/ Benzino & Dave Mays
itunes:title: Episode 10 w/ Benzino & Dave Mays
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. Drink Champs is a weekly podcast and in episode 10 the guys drink it up with Benzino and Dave Mays formerly of The Source Magazine. The guys drink it up and discuss the history of the Source magazine, the Source awards, Almighty RSO, Love & hip hop tv show, hip hop weekly magazine, and a lot more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
